<span id="freeTextContainer12047515591976172234">I&apos;m taking a break from this book. It&apos;s not long, but it&apos;s been kind of a slog for me, and I have trouble getting very far at a stretch. The information is relatively interesting, but the writing seems to wander around, almost verging on &quot;filler&quot; at times. It also has the timbre of a condescending talk-radio monologue; it&apos;s sprinkled with asides that might have been framed as interesting comparisons, but instead come across as prissy freshman self-righteousness. I might finish it later, maybe I&apos;</span>
